                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the King, Patriarch and
                           Metropolitan; headings and incipits of the texts; directives for the
                           ministers; the word ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡; most of the abbreviations; elements of the
                           punctuation signs and Ethiopic numerals.
 
 Incipits of most of
                           the Anaphoras are written alternately in red and black lines (s. fols.
                           43ra, 54ra, 59rb, etc.).</seg>
                     </handNote>
